R U P A L I   H A S I J A

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
For the last many years of knowing each other, @arjun.sen and I would always talk about starting and building something which we could call our own. This really wasn’t an overnight idea or something we thought of doing randomly. It’s a dream which has lived within us for a few years now but it always felt a little too scary and big. 
We really kept on delaying it because honestly we didn’t know how to do it with no outside help, no business affiliates or business families involved, or any experience of how to run a business!

But, 7 months ago we took a leap of faith and we set out on this journey from the ground up, just the two of us with one idea in mind. And, the good part was that this was a familiar feeling…we knew it all too well from the first time we started a YouTube Channel. Just the 2 of us figuring things out one thing at a time..one step at a time with real hard work and honesty.

It has taken a long time of “a lot of us“ to turn this idea into a reality. ON THIS AUSPICIOUS DAY OF DIWALI WE CAN FINALLY SHARE WITH YOU THAT WE ARE LAUNCHING OUR OWN BRAND IN DECEMBER 2021! 
We hope and pray that you will give this your love and blessings. We made sure and are constantly going to make sure that we put our heart and soul into it so that you get the best of everything. As much as this is ours…now it’s yours too! We’re forever grateful for all your love and support 🙏🏻❤️

MORE DETAILS WILL BE OUT SOON! Stay tuned…

latestIgtvVideos.title: WINE & PINK LOOK WITH KAY BEAUTY EYESHADOW PALETTE
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I tried out the latest @kaybykatrina Eyeshadow Palettes and I really like the how smooth and pigmented these are. The palettes come in 4 variants and I’ve used the “Self Love” Palette for this look.
The packaging is stunning with beautiful artwork created by Gaurvi Sharma and it does come with a mirror inside. 

They’re Enriched with Macadamia Nut Oil and Aloe Vera Oil which help in keeping  the formula non drying and long lasting. 
My absolute favourite are the intensely foiled shimmery shades, they’re stunning on the eyes. Even the Matte shades do blend quickly and beautifully. The range is also Cruelty Free, Paraben Free, Parafin Free, Mineral Oil Free and Dermatologically Tested. 
The quality of these palettes is pretty amazing, do consider check them out ❤️ 

They’re exclusively available at @mynykaa and Nykaa stores.
